data.title: Executive Vice President Zhen Liang Led a Delegation to Visit Universities in Hong Kong and Macao

data.text: [Announced by Harbin Institute of Technology, Shenzhen] (International Affairs Office/Text, Photo) From June 17 to 20, 2019, in order to learn from the successful experiences of universities in Hong Kong and Macao in personnel training, technological innovation and international education, Zhen Liang, Assistant to the President of Harbin Institute of Technology and Executive Vice President of Harbin Institute of Technology, Shenzhen, led a delegation to visit Hong Kong and Macao; They visited the Liaison Office of the Central People's Government in the Macao Special Administrative Region, the University of Hong Kong, the Hong Kong University of science and technology, the Chinese University of Hong Kong and the University of Macau, and had a discussion with representatives of alumni in Hong Kong. (Editor Wu Ruichan)
